                                Versions
                                
Version:

1.0           Basic Quotation. Each quote was limited to 10 lines,
              Separated by a '*'
              
1.01          Quotations can be any length, separated by a '*'

1.02          Same as 1.01, but separated by a '~'. Above versions never
              released
              
