@node Bug
@previous Versions
                             Quotation v1.02
                             
                                 Bug!
                                 
   There was a bug on v1.0 which I have tried to rectify. Sometimes, the
program tries to look past the end of file. Previously, this wasn't checked
for, and therefore, the program kept looking. Now, this should be trapped.
When run, if it goes past the end of file, a number of blank lines will be
displayed.

   If the bug does continue, please write to me, and I will try to rectify
the problem.

@endnode
